OL,3,CTitanic and The Lord of the Rings
OL,4,Cactor Bernard Hill dies aged 79
OL,6,FThe actor played Captain Edward Smith
OL,7,Fin the Oscar-winning 1997 epic romance
OL,8,FTitanic, which starred Leonardo
OL,9,FDiCaprio and Kate Winslet.
OL,11,FHe also portrayed Theoden, King of
OL,12,FRohan, in The Lord Of The Rings
OL,13,Ftrilogy directed by Sir Peter Jackson.
OL,15,FHill joined the Lord Of The Rings cast
OL,16,Ffor the second film in the trilogy,
OL,17,F2002's The Two Towers, which won two
OL,18,FAcademy Awards for best sound editing
OL,19,Fand best visual effects.
