OL,3,CTitanic and The Lord of the Rings
OL,4,Cactor Bernard Hill dies aged 79
OL,6,FHe returned to the franchise for
OL,7,F2003's The Return Of The King, which
OL,8,Fpicked up 11 Oscars, including best
OL,9,Fpicture and best director for Sir
OL,10,FPeter.
OL,12,FHill also starred in drama series Boys
OL,13,FFrom The Blackstuff, and the 2015 BBC
OL,14,Fadaptation of Hilary Mantel's novel
OL,15,FWolf Hall.
OL,17,FThe BBC described him as an
OL,18,F"incredible talent" who "blazed a
OL,19,Ftrail across the screen" during his
OL,20,Fcareer.
