OL,6,FActress and musician Barbara Dickson,
OL,7,Fwho starred with him in a musical
OL,8,Fbased on the Beatles, was among those
OL,9,Fpaying tribute, describing him as a
OL,10,F"marvellous actor".
OL,12,FAlongside a photo of them together,
OL,13,Fshe wrote: "It's with great sadness
OL,14,Fthat I note the death of Bernard Hill.
OL,16,F"We worked together in John, Paul,
OL,17,FGeorge, Ringo and Bert, (by) Willy
OL,18,FRussell marvellous show 1974-1975.
